	<td class="alt1" id="td_post_1168544">
	
		
		<!-- message -->
		<div id="post_message_1168544">
                  
                  These are my suggested 4 barriers that would allow the sorcerer to change how they are fighting in combat. <br />
<br />
One is best for when energy and agro is not a concern, another is better for normal combat because of its efficiency and protection, another is better for solo or for dealing damage early on in the fight before agro has been solidified, and another is better for fighting very hard spell casters.<br />
<br />
<br />
<font size="4"><font color="Red">Fire Barrier</font></font><br />
This Barrier would be our &quot;burn&quot; dps option.<br />
<br />
<br />
* 15% increase to all spell damage, but 35% increase in energy cost<br />
* 20% increase in casting speed and range of spells.<br />
* 30% damage return shield (if we're hit for 1000, returns 300)<br />
<br />
<font size="4"><font color="Magenta">Force Barrier</font></font><br />
This Barrier would be our efficient and defensive dps option.<br />
<br />
<br />
* 15% chance for spell to cost 50% less energy<br />
* Prevents AOE except when we are the target of the aoe.<br />
* 30% Increases Armor class<br />
<br />
<font size="4"><font color="Cyan">Frost Barrier</font></font><br />
This Barrier would be our subtle and preservation dps option.<br />
<br />
* 15% less damage, but spells generate 75% less hate.<br />
* 50% increase to duration of all cold spell effects<br />
* 30% damage rune with 25% chance to stun attackers for 3 seconds in a block of ice.<br />
<br />
<font size="4"><font color="Red">C</font><font color="Orange">h</font><font color="Yellow">r</font><font color="Green">o</font><font color="Blue">m</font><font color="Indigo">a</font><font color="Purple">t</font><font color="Red">i</font><font color="Orange">c</font> Barrier</font><br />
This Barrier would be our anti-spell dps option.<br />
<br />
* 25% chance to reflect spells cast on sorcerer.<br />
* 50% spell rune on sorcerer, 25% group wide, absorbs damage into energy.<br />
* Sorcerer is is immune to Stun, Interuption, and Counter Spells.<br />
* 100% Spell Identification, 50% more likely to Disperse, Reflect, or Dispell.<br />
<br />
<br />
Thoughts?
                  
		</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
		
		
		
		
		<!-- edit note -->
			<div class="smallfont">			<hr size="1" style="color:#330066" />
				<em>
				Last edited by jhorry : June 23rd, 2007 at <span class="time">05:42 PM</span>.
				
				</em>
			</div>
		<!-- / edit note -->
		
	
	</td>
</tr>
