				<div style="font-style:italic">I'm positive, Jhorry has been proposing ideas for class flavor since he started posting here.  I can plainly see he wants more options as a sorceror and not to be so one dimensional, and while I dont agree with his ideas, I do agree with adding more things or ways to deal damage than there currently is.<br /></div>
			
